snippet.description:
✅  After three weeks of hearings, Johnny Depp's libel case against a British tabloid has come to a close. However, for Amber Heard, those three weeks were "incredibly painful." RELATED: Lawyer Claims Johnny Depp Was Misogynistic Abuser Of Ex-Wife Amber Heard The "Pirates of the Caribbean" star was suing News Group Newspapers, publisher of the Sun,…
